derivation.yuyuan_name: late Middle English: from Latin indubitabilis, from in- 'not' + dubitabilis (see dubitable)

entry.tran: 明确无疑的;毋庸置疑的
entry.def: You use indubitable to describe something when you want to emphasize that it is definite and cannot be doubted.
